cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

The paper proposes an algorithm for real-time 6DOF pose tracking of rigid 3D objects using a monocular RGB camera, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) categories. The paper also proposes a novel dataset for monocular object pose tracking, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and multimedia (cs.MM) categories.
